nodes.text: Dark Times—Out of the Wilderness 1 was the eighteenth issue of the Star Wars: Dark Times comic series and the first in the Out of the Wilderness story arc. It was first announced in Star Wars Insider 124 and was published in August of 2011.

Darth Vader confronts a deadly assassin . . .
. . . the outlaw crew of the Uhumele arrives at the scene of Jedi Dass Jennir's last adventure—but Jennir is already gone . . .
. . . and half a galaxy away, Imperial fighters are shot out of the sky by an “unarmed” pleasure craft . . .
